-- Lebanon's Blom Bank says 2013 net profit up 5 pct at $353 mln
-- By Dominic Evans
-- Fri Jan 31, 2014 02:19AM EST
-- None



BEIRUT, Jan 31 (Reuters) - Lebanon's Blom Bank <BLOM.BY> reported net profit up 5 percent last year to $353 million despite what it said were difficult conditions in Lebanon, which has suffered an economic slowdown since the 2011 outbreak of conflict in neighbouring Syria.

